Staying safe out there?
Feel free to come back any time you need some rest.

I run this humble outpost along with some fellow researchers.
Do take some time to introduce yourself around here.
Ah, silly me, you'll need some of these to handle the local wildlife.

Maybe  try talking to Carl down by the tents?

Sorry. Busy.
